text: Jesse McCartney (born April 9, 1987) is an American singer-songwriter, and actor. He is known for his work in All My Children as JR Chandler. He was also part of the boy band Dream Street. McCartney also is known for voicing Theodore in Alvin and the Chipmunks and Roxas in Kingdom Hearts. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:American pop singers Category:American rock singers Category:American R&B; singers Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Singer-songwriters from New York City Category:Actors from New York City
